ry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPs一齊左就兩年"},{"pid":"22484255913b9e1cff49cd7828095ed33b593b1b","tid":91501,"uid":21402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>時間耐左放低晒咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔得 感覺好怪</blockquote><br />\n同佢講你最近點呀？<br />\n假撚到...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9986ccaae1238e53c2bbe0aa05977ca3adbb172b","tid":91501,"uid":21402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T04:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好痴線人啦,分左手做乜撚野Frd <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做到frd既只有2個原因<br />\n1) 當初冇愛過對方<br />\n2) 仲愛緊對方</blockquote><br />\n2？仲愛緊對都未必做到朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad42fd310fd7082d9636929636e53990f70252a","tid":91501,"uid":21402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識得有啲女 比人飛左仲成日約人出黎食飯 話咩再見亦是朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁又係既 閪痕呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔話做朋友點做sp繼續比人屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爭住做免費雞究竟係咩心態？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都好想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766289ddf68656b3d82aaf9cf9fa268df6b3500a","tid":91501,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T07:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>時間耐左放低晒咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔得 感覺好怪</blockquote><br />\n同佢講你最近點呀？<br />\n假撚到...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockqu